$ \Omega = \{ \omega = (T_0,X_0), (T_1,X_1),...) \}, $

  • $T_i$ - $i$- ,
  • $X_i$ - : $X_i \in \{Arrive, Depart \}$

$L$ -

$W$ -

$W_q$ -

$L_q$ -

$ L= \sum_{k=0}^{\infty}k\Pi_k = \frac{\alpha\lambda}{\mu - \alpha\lambda} $

$ W= \frac{L}{\alpha\lambda} $

$ W_q= W - \frac{1}{\mu}$

$ L_q = \alpha\lambda W_q$

1. $\frac{\alpha\lambda}{\mu} < 1$¶

  • $\alpha = 0.7 $
  • $\lambda = 3$
  • $\mu = 4$

$ L= \frac{3 * 0.7}{4-3 * 0.7} = 1.105$

$ W= \frac{1.105}{3 * 0.7} = 0.526$

$ W_q= 0.526 - \frac{1}{4} = 0.276 $

$ L_q= 3*0.7*0.276 = 0.5796 $
